"{\"uid\": \"windsorstar.com-news-local-news-fierce-intimidating-windsor-chef-team-canada-take-world-culinary-olympics-gold\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"You can save this article by registering for freehere.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 54, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Orsign-inif you have an account.\", \"from\": 55, \"to\": 87, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an epic battle of blades, blow torches, and offset spatulas.\", \"from\": 89, \"to\": 156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe now to read the latest news in your city and across Canada.\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 220, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999504325, \"rank\": 4.938659844434298e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe now to read the latest news in your city and across Canada.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999504325, \"rank\": 4.938659844434298e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Create an account or sign in to continue with your reading experience.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Create an account or sign in to continue with your reading experience.\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Windsor chef Adelina Sisti-DeBlasis is among the elite members of Culinary Team Canada, who recently returned from the World Culinary Olympics with gold and silver medals.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9967047221324979, \"rank\": 0.002983103573391, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Culinary Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every four years the world's best chefs don their aprons for the six-day competition in Stuttgart, Germany, where dreams of national pride and the perfect menu can rise and fall like an overbaked souffl\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 705, \"end\": 714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"score\": 0.99999999990996, \"rank\": 4.601052451600605e-11, \"text\": \"Stuttgart\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\"}, {\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9996769182583838, \"rank\": 0.00032142671219068775, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The medals are another feather in the chef's toque for Sisti-DeBlasis, who was named National Chef of the Year in 2023 by the Culinary Federation of Canada.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was her first trip to the Olympics of fine cuisine.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The competition is fierce.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very intimidating at first,\\\" said Sisti-DeBlasis, also a hospitality, tourism and co-op teacher for the GreaterEssex CountyDistrict School Board.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So for my first, to bring home a gold is pretty exciting.\\\"\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Exhibition of Culinary Art, better known as the World Culinary Olympics, ran Feb. 2 to 7.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Culinary Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the largest international culinary arts event on the planet.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Canada won gold in the Restaurant of Nations category, which required teams to prepare a three-course meal for 110 guests.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9967047221324979, \"rank\": 0.002983103573391, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also took silver in the Chef's Table category, preparing a seven-course menu for 14 people.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Overall, Canada ranked sixth in the world out of 24 teams.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1691, \"end\": 1697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999504325, \"rank\": 4.938659844434298e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sisti-DeBlasis was part of the Canadian squad's management team.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_Rugby_World_Cup_squads\", \"score\": 0.7091201068179762, \"rank\": 0.41019834353144224, \"text\": \"Canadian squad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_Rugby_World_Cup_squads\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_Rugby_World_Cup_squads\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her jobs included communications, finance, administration, flavour critique, and recipe editor.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The vast Canuck-inspired menu included pine ice cream, Quebec First Nations spices, Newfoundland salt, sturgeon bacon, maple syrup, sea buckthorn berries, morel mushrooms, and bison.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1959, \"end\": 1965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quebec\", \"score\": 0.9999903267625466, \"rank\": 8.006031403533265e-06, \"text\": \"Quebec\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quebec\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quebec\"}, {\"begin\": 1966, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_peoples_in_Canada\", \"score\": 0.589414469195676, \"rank\": 0.6964858578708942, \"text\": \"First Nations\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_peoples_in_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_peoples_in_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 1988, \"end\": 2000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newfoundland_and_Labrador\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 1.8480778388548543e-12, \"text\": \"Newfoundland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newfoundland_and_Labrador\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newfoundland_and_Labrador\"}, {\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morchella\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"morel mushrooms\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morchella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morchella\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We used the boreal forest as our backdrop,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were very unique flavours that were reminiscent of Canada.\\\"\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2201, \"end\": 2207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999504325, \"rank\": 4.938659844434298e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Overall, Finland won gold, Switzerland took silver, and the bronze went to Iceland.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2220, \"end\": 2227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"score\": 0.9999999814099285, \"rank\": 1.8458775591539727e-08, \"text\": \"Finland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\"}, {\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9999999850756468, \"rank\": 1.4760449325738162e-08, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 2286, \"end\": 2293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iceland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.565035597306616e-14, \"text\": \"Iceland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iceland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iceland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The national team from host country Germany finished behind Canada in ninth place.\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2331, \"end\": 2338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9996769182583838, \"rank\": 0.00032142671219068775, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 2355, \"end\": 2361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999504325, \"rank\": 4.938659844434298e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sixth overall is very impressive because I believe we are the only North American team to make the Top 10,\\\" said Sisti-DeBlasis.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2453, \"end\": 2461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998715015945, \"rank\": 1.2599746495349896e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That feels fantastic.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a decade or more for a national team to bring home a gold medal in Restaurant of Nations.\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was very cool that that happened.\\\"\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sisti-DeBlasis said the European teams that consistently take the podium have a major advantage the Canadians do not - government funding.\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's hard to get to the podium with them,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But this year we were extremely close.\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That speaks volumes that Canada is a force to be reckoned with.\\\"\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2932, \"end\": 2938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999504325, \"rank\": 4.938659844434298e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike other countries, the Canadians have to do fundraisers and search for sponsors.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They also volunteer their time.\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's a lot of time.\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team members travelled from across Canada for five-day practice runs, usually in Toronto, every eight weeks for the last four years.\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3155, \"end\": 3161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999504325, \"rank\": 4.938659844434298e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 3201, \"end\": 3208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.470949565550982e-20, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sisti-DeBlasis said she was grateful for the \\\"unwavering support\\\" of her family.\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not easy to be away so often,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They were so encouraging and excited to see the awesome results of this four-year commitment.\\\"\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For as long as Sisti-DeBlasis can remember, food has consumed her life.\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Food is sustainability,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We can not survive without it.\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's important for us to kind of step back and be thankful and grateful for all the fruits that are around us.\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our lands are able to provide so much for us.\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as we treat it good, it will treat us better.\\\"\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sisti-DeBlasis was only seven years old when she created her first cookbook.\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It included the groundbreaking recipe for Lemon Spree, her crisp and complex combination of lemonade, 7 Up, and a lemon twist.\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 4042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3964, \"end\": 3969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spree_(river)\", \"score\": 0.9986197446498312, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Spree\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spree_(river)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spree_(river)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And just thinking I was a rockstar chef at seven years old.\\\"\", \"from\": 4044, \"to\": 4105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That passion was fostered by her late mother and father, Immacolata and Ferruccio Sisti.\", \"from\": 4107, \"to\": 4195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4164, \"end\": 4174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immaculate_Conception\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.259004373609916e-27, \"text\": \"Immacolata\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immaculate_Conception\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immaculate_Conception\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My mom was an excellent cook at the Ciociaro Club,\\\" said Sisti-DeBlasis.\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I loved watching her cook, sitting beside her and learning all the different techniques that she would do.\", \"from\": 4271, \"to\": 4378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I caught the bug from her.\", \"from\": 4380, \"to\": 4407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subsequently, dad was a fantastic cook after my mom passed away.\", \"from\": 4408, \"to\": 4472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just wanting to experiment and do different and unique things.\\\"\", \"from\": 4473, \"to\": 4536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She said her parents would have been \\\"completely elated\\\" to see how well Team Canada did.\", \"from\": 4538, \"to\": 4627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4611, \"end\": 4622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9967047221324979, \"rank\": 0.002983103573391, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was my first stop when I arrived back from Germany, I went to the cemetery to show them some cool hardware,\\\" said Sisti-DeBlasis.\", \"from\": 4629, \"to\": 4764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4678, \"end\": 4685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9996769182583838, \"rank\": 0.00032142671219068775, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By bringing medals home to Windsor-Essex, and teaching young people to develop skills and dream big, she hopes to stir up the same passion in others that her parents inspired for her.\", \"from\": 4766, \"to\": 4949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4793, \"end\": 4806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Windsor,_Ontario\", \"score\": 0.9269787567716467, \"rank\": 0.07838983050849824, \"text\": \"Windsor-Essex\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Windsor,_Ontario\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Windsor,_Ontario\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love teaching and I love cooking,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4951, \"to\": 4998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the more involved you are in your community, the more you will get out of whatever it is that you do.\", \"from\": 4999, \"to\": 5109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, it's a no-brainer.\", \"from\": 5111, \"to\": 5138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Food is passion.\", \"from\": 5139, \"to\": 5155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Passion is food.\", \"from\": 5156, \"to\": 5172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being able to get students excited about cooking, and maybe doing that for a living, is a win-win for everybody.\\\"\", \"from\": 5174, \"to\": 5288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"twilhelm@postmedia.com  Postmedia is committed to maintaining a lively but civil forum for discussion.\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5314, \"end\": 5323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Postmedia\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please keep comments relevant and respectful.\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Comments may take up to an hour to appear on the site.\", \"from\": 5439, \"to\": 5493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will receive an email if there is a reply to your comment, an update to a thread you follow or if a user you follow comments.\", \"from\": 5494, \"to\": 5623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Visit ourCommunity Guidelinesfor more information.\", \"from\": 5624, \"to\": 5674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"365 Bloor Street East, Toronto, Ontario, M4W 3L4  \\u00a9 2025 Windsor Star, a division of Postmedia Network Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 5676, \"to\": 5804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5761, \"end\": 5783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Postmedia Network Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unauthorized distribution, transmission or republication strictly prohibited.\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 5882, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This website uses cookies to personalize your content (including ads), and allows us to analyze our traffic.\", \"from\": 5884, \"to\": 5992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more aboutcookies here.\", \"from\": 5993, \"to\": 6021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By continuing to use our site, you agree to ourTerms of UseandPrivacy Policy.\", \"from\": 6022, \"to\": 6099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can manage saved articles in your account.\", \"from\": 6101, \"to\": 6147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"and save up to 100 articles!\", \"from\": 6149, \"to\": 6177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can manage your saved articles in youraccountand clicking the X located at the bottom right of the article.\", \"from\": 6179, \"to\": 6290, \"entities\": []}]}"